snippet.title: Monsta Teaser - The Vision of The Orb from Prophet
snippet.description:
Looks like the Prophet Monsta left you guys his trusty orb! Use it to view the visions from the future and get the hints you will need for the future of Monsta Infinite!

Be sure to subscribe to our newsletter to not miss a single thing!

Check out our official platforms to get the latest news and updates!
